title: Murderer who escaped prison has stolen a van and changed his appearance, US police say
description: A convicted murderer who escaped from prison last month has been spotted and has changed his appearance, police in the US have said.

description: Spanish FA president Luis Rubiales has said he will resign after he kissed a player following the country's Women's World Cup win.

description: A few months ago, my friend drove through Amizmiz on holiday.

title: Manchester United winger Antony put on leave of absence after assault claims by three women

title: 16-year-old Palestinian boy 'shot dead by Israeli army'

title: Earthquake survivors sleep rough as rescuers battle to save people trapped in remote areas
description: Thousands of people who survived the Morocco earthquake have spent the night sleeping rough - with many losing their homes or too fearful to head indoors.
